div.p:
How to Apply: Candidates are required to apply online at https://www.princeton.edu/acad-positions/position/28321 and submit the following documents:
1. A cover letter with summary of proposed research project (200 words);
2. A research proposal (1500 words), including description and significance, bibliography, and timetable;
3. A current curriculum vitae;
4. A scholarly paper or dissertation chapter (not to exceed 10,000 words) that best represents the candidate's scholarly achievement or potential;
5. Contact information for two references.
